Femi Emiola https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Femi_Emiola 0 Femi Emiola is an American actress. She is best known for her roles in the TV series Wicked Wicked Games and in the web series If Looks Could Kill. Her first name is a Yoruba translation pronounced "F-eh-mi" meaning "love me" or "marry me". Femi_Emiola is an_American_actress .
